    <item>
      <title>Northern Star 将以 50 亿澳元收购 De Grey Mining 黄金业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/northern-star-to-buy-de-grey-in-deal-valued-at-a-5-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在贵金属价格飙升的背景下，黄金生产商寻求获得更多供应，Northern Star Resources Ltd. 已同意以约 50 亿澳元（33 亿美元）的价格收购 De Grey Mining Ltd.。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/northern-star-to-buy-de-grey-in-deal-valued-at-a-5-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 21:36:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中西部寒流来袭 北极降雪影响假日旅游</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/arctic-blast-of-midwest-cold-snow-imperils-post-holiday-travel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据美国气象预报中心预测，未来两天一股北极寒流和大雪将席卷五大湖地区，造成危险天气，可能会扰乱数百万人的公路和航空出行计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/arctic-blast-of-midwest-cold-snow-imperils-post-holiday-travel</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 20:31:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>挪威内阁盟友阻止深海采矿许可发放至 2026 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/norway-cabinet-ally-blocks-deep-sea-mining-licensing-until-2026</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为确保挪威政府预算在议会获得通过的协议的一部分，挪威政府开放海底采矿的计划已被搁置。]]></description>
